description: Leo Forte"The Force"Ht: 5'9" WT: 175lbs Lifetime W/L record ( 9-4)Randall O'Reilly"The Rock"Ht: 5'8" WT: 150lbsSeason W/L record (2-2) Patrick "Ricochet" Rouge was intended to fight in our last semifinal match of the Summer Smackdown Tournament, unfortunately he was unable to fight so stepping up to the plate is Randall "The Rock" O'Reilly. "The Rock" has fought many opponents and now one of NK's finest veterans, Leo "The Force" Forte, stands in his way. Although "The Force" has been away from the mat, he's cocky as ever and walks in determined to win. After three action packed rounds, find out who secures their spot in hopes to win the championship belt, while the other is treated like an animal, getting tossed around and fucked like a rag doll before having his face covered in cum.
title: Last Semifinal Match of Naked Kombat's Summer Smackdown Tournament!
